text: Myint Naing is a Burmese politician. Myint Naing may also refer to: *Htun Myint Naing, Burmese businessman *Myint Naing (artist) (born 1967), Myanmar watercolour artist *Myint Naing (professor) (born 1942), Burmese dental professor *Myint Naing (MP) (born 1968), Burmese politician
title: Myint Naing (disambiguation)
